@Lewis - I don’t know why is has taken me so long reading your best of the week posts to come to realize this:
since your recap of last week’s top five comes out in the comments for Monday puzzle, they do a service to early-week solvers who are likely to drop by and see them. Showing the range of clever and creative clues, and considering how a clue and answer relate, all invite newer solvers into the wider world of crossword play. 

Thanks for curating them as carefully as you do!

